data.title: National Centers for Environmental Information (NCEI)
data.text: Free access to NCEI's archive of global coastal, oceanographic, geophysical, climate and historical weather data. These data include quality controlled daily, monthly, seasonal, and yearly measurements of temperature, precipitation, wind, degree days, ocean profiles, ocean circulation, ocean salinity, sea level, and solar observatories as well as a variety of radar, satellite, model and 30-year Climate Normals data. Customers can also order most of these data as certified hard copies for legal use.
